require sedation, neuromuscular paralysis, intubation, and mechanical ventilation in addition to the other measures.', 'Synergism', 'Caution is advised if 5-HT3 receptor antagonists are prescribed in combination with SSRIs.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/179255/', '', 'Rolapitant', 'Viloxazine, Esketamine', 1767369485);
